  <h2 class="sh">What the pipeline produces<br><em>in practice.</em></h2>
  <p class="lead" style="margin-top:.5rem;font-size:13.5px">Two production-ready itineraries, designed by the AI planning pipeline, uploaded to Wetu, and synced to Shopify. Each has a client-facing view and a separate operator-facing operations view with full logistics detail not visible to guests.</p>

