<!-- WETU GAP TABLE -->
<section class="section">
  <span class="annot">The gap Plekify fills</span>
  <h2 class="sh">Wetu handles itinerary presentation.<br><em>Plekify adds the commerce layer.</em></h2>
  <table class="gap-table">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>When a guest…</th><th>Wetu today</th><th>With Plekify on Shopify</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Clicks "Book Now"</td><td class="wetu">Email sent to consultant — no online payment</td><td class="plek">Shopify checkout with deposit or instalment payment</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Views the itinerary</td><td class="wetu">wetu.com subdomain — not the operator's domain</td><td class="plek">Operator's own branded domain</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Asks about pricing</td><td class="wetu">Static price display only — no booking capability</td><td class="plek">Static display on Shopify, plus live checkout when PMS is connected</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Google crawls the page</td><td class="wetu">Nothing — JS iframe, not indexed by search engines</td><td class="plek">Full HTML, structured data, automatic sitemap</td></tr>
      <tr><td>AI agent queries inventory</td><td class="wetu">Not discoverable by AI assistants</td><td class="plek">Queryable via Shopify Catalog API and UCP</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Abandons without booking</td><td class="wetu">No recovery possible</td><td class="plek">Automated Shopify abandoned checkout recovery</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Browses property detail</td><td class="wetu">Description and images</td><td class="plek">Rooms, dining, activities, spa, rates — each browseable</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Wants to book accommodation</td><td class="wetu">No booking capability — Wetu is a presentation tool</td><td class="plek">Live availability, real-time pricing, on-domain checkout</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Requests another language</td><td class="wetu">Wetu offers some itinerary translation; the wider site does not translate</td><td class="plek">20+ languages across the entire Shopify storefront via Markets</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Wants local currency pricing</td><td class="wetu">Static display only — no currency conversion at checkout</td><td class="plek">130+ currencies, localised pricing at checkout</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

